Available Tools: get_forecast_daily | get_forecast_hourly | get_forecast_weekly
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "days": number, "unit": "string" }
Response Schema: { "location": "string", "forecast": [{ "date": "string", "high": number, "low": number, "condition": "string" }] }
---
Question: Can you provide the hourly weather prediction for Austin over the next day?
Call: { "func_call": "get_forecast_hourly", "location": "Austin, TX", "days": 1, "unit": "imperial" }
Response: { "location": "Austin, TX", "forecast": [{ "date": "2023-11-05T10:00:00", "high": 72, "low": 65, "condition": "Sunny", "precipitation_probability": 5 }, { "date": "2023-11-05T11:00:00", "high": 75, "low": 67, "condition": "Sunny", "precipitation_probability": 0 }, { "date": "2023-11-05T12:00:00", "high": 78, "low": 69, "condition": "Partly Cloudy", "precipitation_probability": 10 }] }

